{"tid":271814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實日本係各方面完勝韓國","createTime":"2017-06-05T11:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T13:17:31.000Z","uid":9957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84943562cb8e969a41edcb3db12e8f29522e30e1","tid":271814,"uid":9957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:12:26.000Z","msg":"日本料理冇一樣係唔好食 就算係日本7仔既便當都屌打香港大部分餐廳既嘢食<br />\n韓國料理我真係唔識欣賞 將啲最低級既食材撈埋一齊食 咩部隊鍋真係狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n日本人有禮貌好多 啲sales唔會西面白鴿眼 特別啲姐姐笑得好甜又溫柔 <br />\n韓國啲女人粗魯冇文化 其實就同大陸婆冇乜分別 係整咗容加舊barcode劉海烈焰紅唇咁姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n科技方面 日本汽車電器牌子都係好受歡迎 你幾時會聽到有人話要買韓國電器同車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到有特色既建築物 日本有姬路城 嚴島神社 清水寺 白川鄉 多多都數唔曬<br />\n韓國?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到今時今日仲見到有人哈韓真係睇唔透"},{"pid":"dc7ab3fba28a941493d1a189c2115f35c87889f0","tid":271814,"uid":86438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"韓國真係請我都唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2277342508df5904344219e1a0d9b082628f6a78","tid":271814,"uid":9957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韓國真係請我都唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n狗也不屌"}]}